<h2 id="section-format">N1 Reading Section Format and Structure</h2>
  <p>The JLPT N1 reading section (読解 dokkai) is the longest and most demanding part of the test. With 110 minutes to handle multiple passage types, understanding the structure lets you plan your time and energy strategically.</p>

