      <strong>⏱️ Watch the Clock</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Check time after each passage type. If you are behind, skip to information retrieval (easiest points) and come back to long passages.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #fefce8; border-left: 4px solid #eab308; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
      <strong>✏️ Mark and Return</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">If unsure about a question, mark your best guess and flag it. Return during the review phase. A guess is always better than a blank.</p>
